snippet.title: Fear Unlimited
snippet.description: Fear Unlimited was an old flash games that I used to play back in the year 2009. So seeing how Adobe decided to end game itself at the end of the year of 2020. I picked something up that allows everyone to play old flash games. So, I've decided to give off a play through of the entire thing about the flash game itself. And also, one thing to mention. I do NOT own any music that plays in this old flash game. That credit goes to the original owners of the music such as Rob Zombie and Nemesis Theory. Anywho, Enjoy the video!
